	Name: Sudoku Solver
	Author: Dr. Hyakkimaru#6020

	Recommended
	- Trigger Type: Regex
	- Trigger: `\A(?i)(-|<@!?204255221017214977>)\s*s(udoku)?\s*s(olver)?(\s*|\z)`

	Copyright: 2021 Hyakki999
